==English==
=== Noun ===
'''wallpaper''' (''[[uncountable]]'')

# A decorative paper-like material used to cover the inner walls of buildings.
# (''computing'') An image used to cover and thereby [[personalize]] a [[desktop]].<!--Non-definitional information: Image may be tiled, stretched, or justified.-->

